tasks.details:
Implement minimal-risk fixes in `core/offline-mode-manager.ts` and targeted regression tests. Keep behavior backward-compatible with existing provider chain and runtime profile policy.

Acceptance criteria:
1) sessions are cleaned up/evicted and do not grow unbounded;
2) failed run timing uses consistent wall clock;
3) fallback extraction prioritizes ScoringEngine pruning before semantic fallback;
4) split fallback avoids cutting tags when DOMParser path unavailable/fails;
5) fallback hash collision risk reduced in degraded environments.
6) extractor tests pass.
